{
  "stem": "17761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 114.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But immediately we had to face-- after a very short period, we have to face a number of very severe survival problems.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One was simply food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where do we take food?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then it was the winter coat, clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where to live?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- there are certain periods that I really don't remember even well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just remember living in many places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some place we lived there were about 20, 30, or 40 families in a big hall and we separated with-- with some blankets each little apartment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You call that apartment, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very difficult to live and we have no privacy whatsoever, but you were-- you witnessed everything which happens in life of so many families.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Finally, and this is what I remember best of all, we succeeded in having a little room in a big house called the Casino.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In this house in Mogliev, there were many Jewish families living there, only Jewish families, of the deported Jews of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ghetto started to organize itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a committee, a Jewish committee, who was appointed by the Romanian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were no democratic elections for that, but somehow we tried to organize our life to make it-- decent is too much, but to make it livable, that you could just live in a more-- more or less organized way.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember that I got to my bar mitzvah, which was about a year and a half, a year before we were deported, year and a half or something like this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got a watch, a golden watch from my parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was these watches that had a-- a chain that you put it in your little pocket.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it had a cover of gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I liked it very much, naturally.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
